{"tid":331003,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"呃蝦條都要盜亦有道","createTime":"2017-07-21T17:43:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T14:05:07.000Z","uid":46010,"like":220,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ed088937c56524e4d2c605319b3114494380bad","tid":331003,"uid":46010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:43:15.000Z","msg":"係tg post留底左自己tg之後<br />\n發覺都幾多仲讀緊中學嘅絲打<br />\n報大數/扮巴打去避開d狗公<br />\n搵真心想識朋友嘅人傾計<br />\n多數都係屋企背景唔好<br />\n可能單親或者長期冇人理<br />\n被人中出即飛<br />\n成個人性情大變<br />\n變到好濫交好隨便十個八個sp套都唔戴<br />\n你破人處就爽果幾分鐘<br />\n人地就最少被你影響幾年甚至害人一世<br />\n個個男人都想屌閪係事實<br />\n但唔好揀d心靈脆弱<br />\n又細個嘅學生妹埋手<br />\n屌完block柒人潛水係好容易<br />\n但做人唔該有返基本嘅良知<br />\n為左自己條撚爽一陣害人一世你過意得去?<br />\n係度開得我預左被人話我道德撚<br />\n唔岩聽就請你負評上一頁<br />\n奉勸各位要帶眼識人<br />\n<br />\n剛剛果位絲打我知你睇到<br />\nWish you all the best."},{"pid":"717a6944ad237c7f554a2cb695ac3d0325f665b9","tid":331003,"uid":129248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:49:53.000Z","msg":"啱聽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c81f0f197c94f2a37c88dc49e0069629fac072b","tid":331003,"uid":46010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:51:15.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41a13f281feab2fc6efd678ea4a2ad9caa9bcf3","tid":331003,"uid":14709,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:58:24.000Z","msg":"正評上一頁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係呢到係連燈 mk集中地<br />\n<br />\n講黎都無咩用<br />\n<br />\n係風氣問題"},{"pid":"9e8ced31918f1f7c2447b5f3c9792c5d721d1f79","tid":331003,"uid":46010,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:08:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正評上一頁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係呢到係連燈 mk集中地<br />\n<br />\n講黎都無咩用<br />\n<br />\n係風氣問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔係預班狼睇完會唔食肉<br />\n係想唔開心嘅絲打<br />\n特別係仲讀緊書嘅<br />\n唔好諗住上網識人<br />\n好似有人錫就乜都比哂人<br />\n事實係你只會一直沉淪落去<br />\n比以前更加迷失"},{"pid":"fe6759ce66c0193dc82236698dc0b3e4d1808a94","tid":331003,"uid":46010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:16:59.000Z","msg":"係度講真話冇乜人想聽<br />\n個post過兩日都係會沉<br />\n如果你係我講嘅人<br />\n又有緣見到呢個post嘅<br />\n希望你可以臨崖勒馬"},{"pid":"af607175ea5adc7401085916d866046efa7260c8","tid":331003,"uid":6347,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:20:34.000Z","msg":"比人呃之後就10個8個sp唔用套<br />\n咁係佢自己問題<br />\n呢d人唔抵可憐"},{"pid":"c97dc2b4132434f34d6b655ea4320843daed7d0b","tid":331003,"uid":79128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:20:41.000Z","msg":"正評 幫推"},{"pid":"4e16ff427c30c9c8accf33bcf3fee06d8141a328","tid":331003,"uid":113429,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:21:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09ca711c970320be8600f02f3c408508b3877c08","tid":331003,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:22:15.000Z","msg":"冇入開感情台 但幫推"},{"pid":"87511e64735971dce61cb67ecfcff684b1c29936","tid":331003,"uid":46010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:31:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比人呃之後就10個8個sp唔用套<br />\n咁係佢自己問題<br />\n呢d人唔抵可憐</blockquote><br />\n我都覺得咁被人呃係on9嘅<br />\n不過十幾歲仲讀緊書<br />\n一個唔小心冇左個處<br />\n第二日仲要返學<br />\n又唔可以同人講<br />\n係慘嘅"},{"pid":"87de2e0b3b87b811830c81df0dd1bb7757b2b293","tid":331003,"uid":65400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1866dcfb51bdf85bfc575cfbac3422fede80ee9","tid":331003,"uid":128003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:37:33.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"ef3f017f1ba923686c48b8b3230b8d3bf896eee1","tid":331003,"uid":72258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:50:17.000Z","msg":"默默地留下正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cade583952adec605ec7726dbe1d5a1520b0c3f5","tid":331003,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":